label.value: greater than moderate alcohol consumption history

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which alcohol consumption was more than 2 drinks per day for men and more than 1 drink per day for women.

label.value: duration of greater than moderate alcohol consumption prior to enrollment

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of greater than moderate alcohol consumption (more than 2 drinks per day for a man or more than 1 drink per day for a woman) prior to study enrollment.

label.value: lifelong non-smoker history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there was no or an insignificant level of smoking.

label.value: current smoker history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there is current smoking either on a daily or non-daily basis.

label.value: current reformed smoker for more than 15 years history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there is no current smoking and has not been smoking for more than 15 years.

label.value: current reformed smoker for less than 15 years history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there is no current smoking and has not been smoking for less than 15 years.

label.value: timing of scoring performance status

definition.value: A one-dimensional temporal region during which a cancer patient's performance status (general well-being and activities of daily life) was assessed.

label.value: preoperative performance status score

definition.value: A timing of scoring performance status that occurs prior to an operation to treat cancer.

label.value: pre-adjuvant performance status score

definition.value: A timing of scoring performance status that occurs prior to adjuvant therapy to treat cancer.

label.value: post adjuvant performance status score

definition.value: A timing of scoring performance status that occurs after adjuvant therapy to treat cancer.

label.value: comment from clinical data entry form

definition.value: A textual entity that states additional information relevant to the filling out of a clinical data entry form.

label.value: pill-based hormonal birth control method

definition.value: A birth control method that involves the use of an oral hormone-based contraceptive typically taken as a pill.

label.value: injection-based hormonal birth control method

definition.value: A birth control method that involves the injection of hormones.

label.value: intrauterine device-based hormonal birth control method

definition.value: A birth control method that involves the use of an intrauterine device (IUD) to deliver hormones.

label.value: patch-based hormonal birth control method

definition.value: A birth control method that involves the administration of hormones through a transdermal patch delivery system.

label.value: vaginal ring-based hormonal birth control method

definition.value: A birth control method that involves the administration of hormones through a vaginal ring.

label.value: duration of hormonal birth control use prior to enrollment

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of use of hormonally based birth control prior to enrollment in a study.

label.value: time since last usage of hormonal birth control

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since the participant last used hormonally based birth control.

label.value: comment on the use of hormonally based birth control

definition.value: A textual entity that states additional information relevant to the use of hormonally based birth control.

label.value: duration of hormone replacement therapy prior to enrollment

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of hormone replacement therapy prior to enrollment in a study.

label.value: time since last usage of hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since the participant last used hormonally replacement therapy.

label.value: comment on the use of hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A textual entity that states additional information relevant to the use of hormone replacement therapy.

label.value: comment on exposure to environmental and workplace carcinogens

definition.value: A textual entity that states additional information relevant to the history of exposure to environmental and workplace carcinogens.

label.value: colorectal cancer risk factor

definition.value: A risk factor that is associated with increased likelihood of colorectal cancer.

label.value: high meat diet colorectal cancer risk factor

definition.value: A colorectal cancer risk factor that is having a diet that is high in red meats and processed meats.

label.value: obesity colorectal cancer risk factor

definition.value: A colorectal cancer risk factor that is having been obese.

label.value: Type II diabetes colorectal cancer risk factor

definition.value: A colorectal cancer risk factor that is having Type II diabetes mellitus.

label.value: previous colorectal polyps colorectal cancer risk factor

definition.value: A colorectal cancer risk factor that is having had colorectal polyps.

label.value: familial adenomatous polyposis colorectal cancer risk factor

definition.value: A colorectal cancer risk factor that is having familial adenomatous polyposis or having a family member with familial adenomatous polyposis.

label.value: estrogen alone hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A hormone replacement therapy where the hormone is estrogen.

label.value: estrogen with progestin hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A hormone replacement therapy where the hormones are estrogen and progestin.

label.value: progestin alone hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A hormone replacement therapy where the hormone is progestin.

label.value: testosterone hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A hormone replacement therapy where the hormone is testosterone.

label.value: clinical history of sepsis

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of sepsis.

label.value: clinical history of pneumonia

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of pneumonia.

label.value: clinical history of open wounds

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of open wounds.

label.value: clinical history of high unexplained fever

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of a high unexplained fever .

label.value: clinical history of positive blood cultures

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of positive blood cultures.

label.value: clinical history of abnormal white blood cell levels

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of abnormal white blood cell levels.

label.value: clinical history of fungal infections

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of fungal infections.

label.value: clinical history of ascites

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of the presence of ascites fluid.

label.value: clinical history of cellulitis

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of cellulitis.

label.value: clinical history of blood transfusion in foreign country

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of receiving a blood transfusion while in another country.

label.value: clinical history of human tissue transplant

definition.value: A clinical  history in which there is a history of receiving a human tissue or organ transplant .

label.value: clinical history of animal tissue xenotransplant

definition.value: A clinical  history in which there is a history of receiving an animal tissue or organ xenotransplant.

label.value: clinical history of smallpox vaccination

definition.value: A clinic history in which there is a history  of a recent of smallpox vaccination.

label.value: a clinical history of contact with someone with smallpox

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of contact with someone who recently had smallpox.

label.value: clinical history of dialysis

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of significant regular dialysis treatment.

label.value: clinical history of cancer at death

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a current diagnosis of cancer at death.

label.value: clinical history of cancer within a time period before death

definition.value: A clinical history in which there is a history of cancer diagnosis within a specified time frame.
